<P>
   KOSOVO-SERBS (Belgrade, Yugoslavia) _ A news analysis: More
quickly than the political opponents of Slobodan Milosevic dared
hope, grass-roots dissatisfaction with the Yugoslav president is
surfacing across much of Serbia. By Blaine Harden. With photo and
locator map.
</P>
