guarantees and other incentives to encourage private businesses to
create jobs and housing, President Clinton on Wednesday swept into
the destitute Oglala Lakota Sioux Indian reservation, by many
measures the sickest, most hopeless, most squalid corner of
America. By Peter T. Kilborn.
</P>
