 &HT;    Costs of exotic birds range widely
 &HT;    By Staff reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   DAYTON, Ohio _ The following are prices are for 4- to 6-week-old
babies, hand-fed three times a day. For babies almost weaned and
down to two feedings, add 20 percent. For fully weaned birds add 30
percent.
</P>
