</P>
<P>
   GETAWAY _ ``Unto These Hills'' in Cherokee, N.C., is one of the
oldest of the outdoor historical dramas that dot the landscape of
the South. We talk with some of the Atlanta actors who are in the
show that focuses on the removal of the Cherokees from their native
land. Also, a listing of 15 other historical dramas from Alabama,
Kentucky, Tennesee, Virginia. (Hamilton, Atlanta
