<SLUG> BC-SALTER-COLUMN-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE FIREWORKS OF BIGOTRY 
</HEADLINE>
   Commentary  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEPHANIE SALTER  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO _ On a day that is uniquely ours, a day in which
we are supposed to reflect upon the greatness of this 223-year-old
nation, another disaffected, disturbed, hate-filled white male went
on a violent rampage.
</P>
<P>
   Covering two states in the heart of the country, he used two
illegally purchased handguns to kill an African-American in Skokie,
Ill., and a Korean doctoral student in Bloomington, Ind.
</P>
<P>
   Shooting from behind the wheel of the best-selling American car
(a Ford Taurus), the man wounded nine other members of racial or
ethnic minorities and missed hitting several others.
</P>
<P>
   Then, as so many disaffected, disturbed and hate-filled white
males have done, Benjamin Nathaniel Smith absented himself from the
bloody mess he'd made by sending a bullet through his own chest.
</P>
<P>
   With the remnants of our own holiday weekend still around us _
the spent coals in the Weber bellies, the empty beer bottles in the
trash, the sunburned noses peeling and Old Glory in need of furling
_ how many of us felt shamed by what Smith did on the Fourth of
July?
</P>
<P>
   How many of us white Americans _ people who Smith believed are
inherently better and more deserving than any other group of
Americans _ felt ashamed that he was one of us?
</P>
<P>
   The more likely response was to distance ourselves from Smith as
fast as we could. Yes, he was a child of privilege. Yes, he and his
parents were well educated. Yes, he grew up in an affluent,
predominantly white surburb.
</P>
<P>
   But he was a crazy man. Screwed up. Busted for drugs.
</P>
<P>
   Vociferous white supremacist. Woman batterer. Fanatic.
</P>
<P>
   Abberational.
</P>
<P>
   What if Smith had been black or Jewish? Of Asian, Latino or Arab
descent? What if he had turned his .22-caliber pistol and Bryco
.380 semiautomatic only on innocent bystanders who looked Anglo?
</P>
<P>
   Would we white Americans be so quick to distance the gunman from
his group? How many of us would have felt anger and a need for
vengeance arise? What racial slurs would have sprung to many minds
or lips?
</P>
<P>
   How many law-abiding blacks, Jews, Asian-Americans,
Latino-Americans or Arab-Americans would have been condemned by
sweeping generalizations about ``those people''?
</P>
<P>
   What retaliatory violence _ or mass suspension of civil rights _
might have been considered justified if the targets of hatred had
been white?
</P>
<P>
   Something gave Smith the idea that it was his duty as a white
man to turn talk about driving racial and religious minorities from
the country into reality. Something convinced him that it was a
patriotic, supremely American gesture to stalk black, Asian and
Jewish citizens on the Fourth of July and shoot them down like
dogs.
</P>
<P>
   Shrinks and 12-steppers tell us that, in the individual, shame
is a toxin that must be expelled for our recovery to mental and
emotional health. Religious leaders and ethicists tell us that we
have so purged ourselves of individual shame, there isn't enough
left to inspire collective shame; its absence is a poisonous
deficiency in any healthy society.
</P>
<P>
   Smith felt shame _ that his first name sounded too Jewish, so he
began to call himself ``August.'' Across his chest, he wore a
tattoo: ``Sabbath Breaker.''
</P>
<P>
   In the yearbook of his upscale high school, he chose as his
favorite a Latin quotation: ``Sic semper tyrannis'' _ ``Thus ever
to the tyrants.'' That is the same phrase John Wilkes Booth uttered
after he assassinated President Lincoln.
</P>
<P>
   Benjamin Nathaniel ``August'' Smith. Disaffected, disturbed,
hate-filled murderer. Proud to call himself a white man, proud to
think of himself as one of us.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Stephanie Salter is a columnist for the San Francisco Examiner,
P.O. Box 7260, San Francisco, CA 94120. Her electronic mail address
is salter(at)examiner.com)
</P>
</TEXT>
