<P>
   EUROPE'S HEALTH SCARE: The health scare that has gripped Europe
this year goes far beyond the recent Coca-Cola crisis. Belgium was
an emotional/political/social tinderbox waiting for something like
the naive Coke to come along. A series of scares from Mad Cow
disease to E-coli to Genetically Modified food to dioxin have
people hypersensitive about food in Europe. (Includes 1-column
color graphic illustrating Coke's presence in Europe, 4-column
color photo of man looking for Coke on empty shelves, 2-column
