<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-08 17:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3508 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FEVER-BOOK-REVIEW-NYT     07-08 1120
