</P>
<P>
   BANDWIDTH-TELECOM (Undated) _ All the fuss about bandwidth
ignores one fundamental: All but the final link to your home or
office is a commodity, with rapidly falling prices. Understanding
that may force a rethinking of the telecom business and telecom
stocks. By Seth Schiesel.
