</P>
<P>
   INTERN-FASHIONS (Undated) _ The current crop of female office
interns seems to have no clue about how to dress for success. By
Joanne Gallucci.
</P>
<P>
   CUSTOMS-DECLARE (Undated) _ If, like Florida's First Lady, you
have been known to skirt the rules when bringing back merchandise
from abroad, you may want to mend your ways. The United States
Customs Service estimates that each year, hundreds of thousands of
travelers break the rules, often saying either that they forgot to
pay duties or that they didn't know about them, is making it more
difficult to use ignorance as an excuse for cheating. By Jane
Wolfe.
