that prompted the state Seismic Safety Commission to call for a
review of laws and regulations over school construction and site
approval. Commissioners want to make sure a Belmont fiasco doesn't
happen again as the state is embarking on a big school-building
boom. By Terri Hardy. (Will move in the ``n'' California and ``a''
national news files.)
