a superkid; she's obedient, too, singing the songs and hitting the
marks that are choreographed for her. This season belongs to the
kiddie-pop brigades. Applause is passe; the reaction most eagerly
sought by pop culture right now, from music to television to
movies, is a high-pitched squeal from a mob of young girls. (Nicole
Bengiveno/New York Times Photo)
