<HEADLINE>
BOB BALZER NAMED PUBLISHER AT DAILY BULLETIN IN INLAND EMPIRE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAILY NEWS  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
